Separating you from your way out of there is an extremely wobbly, cricking, and sky-level bridge that's stationed in the middle of a forest canyon.

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:35.220
Now tell me, how are you feeling right at this moment?

00:00:36.220 --> 00:00:39.740
Unless you're Tarzan, you're probably scared out of your mind right now.

